snippet.title: Wizordum - Official Demo Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description: Take a tour of the world, check out gameplay, see enemies, and more in this trailer for Wizordum, an upcoming retro-inspired FPS game. In Wizordum, take the role of a Cleric and fight against Chaos that roams the land--smash, burn, and loot! Wizordum is heading to Early Access in October 2023, and a new demo is available now.
